Consider the following class and static method.

```java
public class Counter {
    private int count;

    public Counter(int c) { count = c; }
    public void increment() { count++; }
    public int getCount() { return count; }
}
```

```java
public static void bump(Counter c) {
    c.increment();
    c.increment();
}
```

What is the value of `myCount.getCount()` after the following code executes?

```java
