Consider the following class and static method.

```java
public class Box {
    private int val;
    public Box(int v) { val = v; }
    public int getVal() { return val; }
    public void setVal(int v) { val = v; }
}
```

```java
public static void process(Box b) {
    b.setVal(b.getVal() * 3);
    b = new Box(0);
}
```

What is the value of `myBox.getVal()` after the following code executes?

```java
Box myBox = new Box(4);
process(myBox);
```

